dc_title_s: Roads and ROW Milwaukee County, WI 2023
dc_description_s: This data represents roads and Right Of Ways (ROW) for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2023. [Roads: Street Centerlines with Address Ranges and Highway Designations, Milwaukee County, WI. ROW: right-of-way boundary lines covering Milwaukee County, Wisconsin]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://gis-mclio.opendata.arcgis.com/
